edu.dhbw.t10.manager.output
Class Output

java.lang.Object
  edu.dhbw.t10.manager.output.Output

public class Output
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides the functionallity of printing Strings via sending Key Strokes to the system. Letters, big letters and numbers are converted directly to their own java.awt.event.KeyEvent constant, which is sent. All other symbols are written via their Unicode. FIXME WIndows support untested Control symbols are sent via their java.awt.event.KeyEvent constant TODO Daniel Get several Control symbols and combine them to a key combination TODO Daniel Get last active window and write there

DanielAl
